content.rendered:
The two brothers, Sam and Dean, have no idea what a dangerous adventure they are embarking on when they set out to find their father, with whom they finally manage to make contact after a long time. Sam Winchester (Jared Padalecki) does his best to uncover the creepy story of his family. Unlike his brother Dean (Jensen Ackles), Sam refuses the head of the family’s obsessive research to expose the sinful force that has taken their mother’s life. Their father’s mysterious phone message leads the Winchester brothers to a California town where unexplained deaths scare residents in fear. They will soon have to face the local legend, the lady in the white dress, the spooky and beautiful hitchhiker who wanders the roads of the area at night, luring young men to their deaths. Their fate takes them to a completely new, creepy world where they have to face unexplained phenomena. The perilous afterlife mission begins in Colorado and leads to the barren farmland of Nebraska, the isolated lakes of Wisconsin, where the laws of nature are turned upside down. Tradition literally comes to life, horror stories and superstitious creatures come to life and keep the countryside in awe.”
Seasons: 15 (2005-2020)
Status: Finished
Creator: Eric Kripke
Channel: The WB The CW
Starring: Shaw Madson, Sterling K. Brown, Chelsea Gilligan
